Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:30.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:37.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:44.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:51.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:01:00.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:05.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:10.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:16.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:22.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号中了 长嘴硬鳞鱼号的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遭到美国联合舰队炮火的 集中攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号受到重创 好不容易得以脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但舰内却在修理时 发生有毒气体外泄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫为了保住全员的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,决定牺牲3名船员 和毒气一同封死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚体认到尼莫的无情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也让强认清科学是种杀人武器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及这艘船正在作战的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:02:02.74,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#16 消失大陆的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼只是想击沉这艘船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且他之前还想夺取蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为有这种东西 才会引起争端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为有这种东西 才会害那么多人送命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号真有那么重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水真有那么重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是舍弃一切 也必须保住蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是那颗石头继承者的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果还得这样痛苦下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我情愿不要这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位都已经知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于刚才的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎部门牺牲了三名同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们的遗骸将送至 我等失去的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本舰将前往纳塔尔海底盆地的 『沉没寺院』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁来帮帮我…拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想请你帮我调查一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头全是细致的纹路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算放大倍率 还是只能看到纹路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还是立体的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这究竟有着什么涵义呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号的装甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是多出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说是世界上最坚硬的金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然能刮伤装甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到它的材质这么坚硬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水 到底是由什么构成的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠我的能力根本无法了解 这到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你 强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我会有这种东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你认为这就是命运吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特他们牺牲了自己的生命 拯救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与生俱来的命运 注定了他们会为此丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使那个人希望继续活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 那些人之所以会死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们之所以会搭上这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我之所以会有这颗 引发一切争端的蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这所有的一切都是命运吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是你与生俱来的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我又是为了什么而活？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了找到这个答案 你得继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须活得这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是蔚蓝之水持有者的命运吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是来看他们的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系 进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你回答我一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特为什么会死？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还有好多事情没教他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有你活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么你能活下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汝乃冒险者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够潜过名为『危险』之瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,探求位于其深处的 传说真相之人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是 就来将吾寻得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全体人员准备举行葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,登陆亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚特兰提斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底竟然会有这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于一万二千年前毁灭的 传说中的大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有任何生物存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是个死亡与寂静的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚特兰提斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么会变成这种废墟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小石子全都是玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且都是些大小差不多的圆形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂了 当时一定非常热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那时热得连石头都熔化了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为我们刚走过的 水晶柱『巴别塔』所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼企图复制出同样的东西 却失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个就是真品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然再也无法启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这座塔的真正用途 并不是破坏性武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那它原本是用来做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,墓园
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,墓园？你怎么晓得？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们称这里为『沉没寺院』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里原本并不是要用来 当作墓园的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久以前 许多亚特兰提斯人 集体在这里丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从那时候起 在返回故乡的那天来临之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里就成了 亚特兰提斯人的暂时墓园
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在与石像鬼的战争中 身亡的同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也都长眠于此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我受够了 不要再说那些了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？测距长 怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来探望一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我以前的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然不是法国红酒 你就将就一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,法国？\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的本名是艾科·韦伦 法国人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾科 那艘船叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱莉丝·勒阿弗尔号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遭到长嘴硬鳞鱼号击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有我一个人被救上鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船…船长的名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劳尔·洛克·拉帝格船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是个很了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你再回答我一个问题好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么你害死那么多人 却还能活得下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总有一天我也会死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 在那之前 我有件事非完成不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,犯了罪的人 必须受到对等的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长背负着沉重的十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他必须代替 众多死去的人们活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为他有件事非完成不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总有一天你会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:17:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果与娜蒂亚的重逢 是为了惩罚船长的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有比这更残酷的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活生生的花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是能够制作出 这么了不起东西的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总有一天还是会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是曾经跟我说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有天一定会制作出 自己的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经没那个必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算把大海整个翻遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算飞到天空的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸他已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发明不是为了要让人 过得更幸福而存在的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还记得我们 第一次见面时的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那时候你曾这么对我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『人生只有一次』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『开心的过吧』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不对啦 是『开心享受』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是我姑丈的口头禅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他真是个好姑丈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会想回勒阿弗尔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你还想继续待在那艘船上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我喜欢鹦鹉螺号上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 我很喜欢他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回去大家那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真了不起 竟然能开在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比石像鬼做出来的人造花 要漂亮多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么做好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想通了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非由我来摘不可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在黑暗中看花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,此乃生命之喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花正是生命的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并且畏惧黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闭上眼即想到黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.77,0:22:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑暗乃不安之帝王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑暗正是死之王国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身处光明之中也不忘黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身处黑暗之中也不忘花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.85,0:22:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不忘那份残忍的麻木
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直视你心中的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畏惧黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闭上眼即想到黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那即是永恒 永不破灭的祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到回归辽阔宇宙的那天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自今日此时起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吾乃黑暗之居民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:23:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将献花于汝等每个人心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祈求安息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:54.75,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:24:02.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:07.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:12.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.44,0:24:21.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:31.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:40.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.27,0:24:44.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.48,0:24:49.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.18,0:24:58.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.37,0:25:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你不打算再飞上天了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.41,0:25:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好想再飞飞看
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.38,0:25:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.58,0:25:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直有个构想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那这次是真的能飞啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.45,0:25:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『强的新发明』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.29,0:25:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
